com.cc.inputs.sensors

Class CCAccelerometer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cc.inputs.sensors.CCAccelerometer

  • public class CCAccelerometer
extends Object
    The class which represents the acceleration of the robot in any given axis X, Y, or Z. Gives the acceleration of the axis in units of Gs.
